---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Mbarek Bikarchalen" description="About Mbarek Bikarchalen Lorem Ipsum">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/at-work.jpg"
					alt="Mbarek Bikarchalen at work with a colleague"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Pathway</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						Passionate full-stack developer, based in Casablanca, with solid experience in <a href="https://laravel.com/">Laravel</a> and <a href="https://reactjs.org/">React.js</a> and <a href="https://vuejs.org/">vue.js</a> to create high-performance web platforms. I have developed solutions for companies like AK Media and Abdelmalek Essaâdi University and Cap Sud Consulting, using modern frameworks and robust databases.
					</p>
					<p>
						Thanks to a master's degree in information systems management, I also possess skills in project management and process optimization. My ability to combine technical development and strategy has allowed me to tackle complex challenges while remaining focused on innovation.					</p>
					<p>
						Versatile and results-oriented, I aim to continue providing digital solutions that meet the needs of businesses, integrating best practices and technologies for quality user experiences.					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<ul>
						<li>
							<strong>Master in Information Systems Management</strong><br>
							Université Abdelmalek Essaâdi, Tétouan, Maroc<br>
							<span>09/2022 - 07/2024</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Professional Bachelor's Degree in Management Information Systems</strong><br>
							Université Abdelmalek Essaâdi, Tétouan, Maroc<br>
							<span>09/2021 - 07/2022</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Higher Technician Certificate in Information Systems Development</strong><br>
							Lycée Technique de l'Excellence, Guelmim, Maroc<br>
							<span>09/2019 - 07/2021</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Below are the key skills I have developed over the years in my academic and professional journey:</p>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Front-End:</strong> bootstrap ,Tailwind ,React.js,Vue.js</li>
						<li><strong>Back-End:</strong> Laravel ,Node.js</li>
						<li><strong>Databases:</strong> mySQL ,MongoDB ,PostgreSQL,SQL Server</li>
						<li><strong>Versionnage:</strong> Git</li>
						
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
			
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
